graphs
Class Cluster

java.lang.Object
  graphs.Cluster
Direct Known Subclasses:
MaximalCluster, RadialCluster
public abstract class Cluster
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class for cluster representation. Methods to manage edges are left to child classes. A cluster is any group of nodes, overlapped or not. For this documentation purposes, cluster, bicluster and group are synonyms, although of course they actually mean very different things.
